The Kebbi State Police Command on Sunday said that it has arrested two men for raping a minor, 12-year-old Hassana Abubakar. According to the police image maker, SP Nafiu Abubakar stated that one Nura Bello 30 years and his accomplice Abdullahi Garba 25 years with the same address lured the minor, Hassana into a tent in their pepper farm and forcefully had canal knowledge of her. SP Nafiu added that upon receipt of the information, the command despatched men who apprehended them immediately and put them in custody, alleging, â€œtheir offence is criminal conspiracy, causing hurt and rape of a minor which contravenes the laws of the land. He noted that the suspects will soon be arraigned for prosecution after proper investigations are concluded on the matter, while appealing to members of the public to continue to give relevant information to the police he said the police remain steadfast and unwavering in their quest to rid the state of criminal elements in the state.